":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ce6a3b7b9b601843902e090d866d234a4381bbdb","tid":1417073,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"咩改號，又中林鄭計，我地岀黎嗌咩做咩都係會同港獨掛勾㗎啦。<br />\n我就講明我係支持香港獨立嘅<br />\n連光復香港都唔比嗌嘅，我下次就攞齊架撐嗌香港獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家係揀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港獨立<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港 時代革命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"大家唔好錯焦點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"8399d41c3c0000dfc2ee01ce7311329486083d3a","tid":1417073,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfba3d67dea636291fc1ba4f5aa4d0d69f0391ff","tid":1417073,"uid":3659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b5ae45d2f2ee5b845f86a6d71264b5b378c1ea0","tid":1417073,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1a97731e67d1d9c54c7b85834d2a336677147e3","tid":1417073,"uid":258578,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"屌！<br />\n<br />\n你嗌完就會有咩？我哋唔好中林奠計呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:31:06.000Z","msg":"中你老母咩<br />\n<br />\n連中國政府都最清楚嘅嘢，香港民主化嘅結果就係香港獨立。中國政權最怕就係呢樣嘢會發生，而喺佢眼中，香港任何民主化嘅活動行為都會標籤做港獨，<br />\n<br />\n咁計法，扣鳩咗幾十年帽啦<br />\n<br />\n十足個奴隸咁，俾個鏈鎖住咗對手廿幾年，然後你每一次想解開佢，個主人就指責你係咪想走佬嘅時候，就對返佢講<br />\n<br />\n「唔係啊，我唔係想走佬啊，我想整鬆少少個鎖等我舒服啲咋」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主人講一句就立即自認低威，覺得做錯嘢<br />\n呢啲咪奴隸心態囉"},{"pid":"326148fb340cc3dd955f1a4d3e33a736c837adbe","tid":1417073,"uid":284585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"